OL,3,CUS submarine sank Iranian warship off
OL,4,Ccoast of Sri Lanka, says defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FA US submarine has sunk an Iranian
OL,8,Fwarship with a torpedo in
OL,9,Finternational waters, US defence
OL,10,Fsecretary Pete Hegseth said.
OL,12,FThe incident in the Indian Ocean off
OL,13,Fthe Sri Lankan coast was the first
OL,14,Fsinking of an enemy vessel by torpedo
OL,15,Fsince the Second World War, Hegseth
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
