OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772647567
OL,3,CUS submarine sank Iranian warship off
OL,4,Ccoast of Sri Lanka, says defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FThe defence secretary did not name the
OL,8,Fship, but earlier Sri Lanka's navy has
OL,9,Fconfirmed that it has rescued 32
OL,10,Fpeople after it received a distress
OL,11,Fcall from Iranian navy ship "IRIS
OL,12,FDena" early this morning.
OL,14,FAbout 140 people remain missing,
OL,15,Fofficials said on Wednesday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
