OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772647567
OL,3,CUS submarine sank Iranian warship off
OL,4,Ccoast of Sri Lanka, says defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FBudhika Sampath, the spokesman of Sri
OL,8,FLanka's navy, earlier said: "Though it
OL,9,Fwas beyond our waters, it was within
OL,10,Four search and rescue region. So we
OL,11,Fwere obliged to respond as per
OL,12,Finternational obligations."
OL,14,FDuring a press conference at the
OL,15,FPentagon on Wednesday after, Hegseth
OL,16,Fsaid: "An American submarine sunk an
OL,17,FIranian warship that thought it was
OL,18,Fsafe in international waters."
OL,20,F"Instead, it was sunk by a torpedo."
OL,26,@xD@GOU|D@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
