OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772647567
OL,3,CUS submarine sank Iranian warship off
OL,4,Ccoast of Sri Lanka, says defence
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,F"The first sinking of an enemy ship by
OL,8,Fa torpedo since World War Two,"
OL,9,FHegseth added.
OL,11,FHegseth also said the US military sank
OL,12,FIran's "prize ship," the "Soleimani" `
OL,13,Fnamed after the former Iranian general
OL,14,FQasem Soleimani who was killed by US
OL,15,Fforces during President Donald Trump's
OL,16,Ffirst term.
OL,18,F"I guess POTUS got him twice," Hegseth
OL,19,Fsaid, referring to Soleimani.
