OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHe added: "We found people floating on
OL,13,Fthe water, rescued them, and later,
OL,14,Fwhen we inquired, we found that those
OL,15,Fpeople are from an Iranian ship."
OL,17,FHe also says that according to the
OL,18,Fdocumentation of the ship 180 people
OL,19,Fare believed to have been on board,
OL,20,Falthough the exact number of missing
OL,21,Fis unknown.
